reviewText: Not watchable in this region. I wished that they would have mentioned that.

This is an adult movie, its only purpose is as a fun skinemax late night outing.  Some twisted freak in Japan edited it for children.  There is literally no nudity of any kind.  Scenes are cropped if necessary so you can only see someone's ear, or failing that, huge digital fog area obliterates entire upper body of actress.  It's a joke worthy of a surrealist.  Global Products seller graciously gave a complete refund.  Did they also edit Deep Throat to be suitable for toddlers?  The *unedited* show itself is very pleasing for what it is - watch it on cinemax.
